    "headline": "Lamb Weston (NYSE:LW) Delivers Impressive Q1 CY2026",
    "summary": "Potato products company Lamb Weston (NYSE:LW) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 2.9% year on year to $1.56 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $6.5 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.72 per share was 17.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
